        <name>XScuTimer_SelfTest</name>
        <param>
          <type><ref refid="struct_x_scu_timer" kindref="compound">XScuTimer</ref> *</type>
          <declname>InstancePtr</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Run a self-test on the timer. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This test clears the timer enable bit in the control register, writes to the timer load register and verifies the value read back matches the value written and restores the control register and the timer load register.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>InstancePtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is a pointer to the <ref refid="struct_x_scu_timer" kindref="compound">XScuTimer</ref> instance.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS if self-test was successful.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_FAILURE if self test was not successful.</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>None. </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
